    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Appointment
    This class defines the Appointment data type that has the instance variables Date, Timeslot, patient, provider.
    ClinicManagerController
    Controller to manage clinic.
    ClinicManagerMain
    Handles launching application.
    Date
    This class defines the Date data type that has the instance variables year, month, and day.
    DateTest
    Test class for the dates class isValid() method
    Doctor
    Class to represent Doctor object, a type of Provider.
    Imaging
    Class to represent imaging objects which contain a radiology variable
    List<E>
    Array-based implementation of "List" data structure to hold list of objects of any type.
    ListTest
    Test class for the List classes add and remove methods
    Location
    Contains (String) County and (String) Zip for each Location.
    Patient
    Contains Patient's Profile, list of completed visits, and charge() calculates charge accrued.
    Person
    Class to represent Person object.
    Profile
    Profile for Patient including Patient's first name, last name, and date of birth.
    ProfileTest
    Testclass for the class profiles compareTo method
    Provider
    Contains (enum) Location and (enum) Specialty for each Provider.
    Radiology
    Contains (String) radiology choices for the imaging class.
    Sort
    Sorts lists of objects in specific order.
    Specialty
    Contains (int) charges for provider's specialty.
    Technician
    Class to represent Technician object, a type of Provider.
    Timeslot
    Contains (int) Hour and (int) Minute for the start time of each.
    Visit
    Defines a node in a singly linked list that maintains the list of Visits per Patient valued with Appointments.
